      <title>Ares 与印尼债务人发生争执，逾 2 亿美元贷款被推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/ares-row-with-indonesia-debtors-over-200-million-loan-delayed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡一家法院推迟了阿瑞斯管理公司 (Ares Management Corp.) 和其他贷款机构因藐视法庭指控而对印度尼西亚商人戴维·萨利姆 (David Salim) 提起的诉讼的听证会，这是他们围绕一笔 2 亿美元贷款展开的长期法律斗争的最新转折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/ares-row-with-indonesia-debtors-over-200-million-loan-delayed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
